text:
Sri Lanka is experiencing adverse weather conditions due to cyclone ditwah. Terrible flooding has gripped the country, with countless people displaced and a slowly rising death toll.
This is an opportunity for us to come together and help those affected. Many organizations and exemplary individuals are leading the charge with food and dry rations. Letâ€™s help them in any way we can.

@amaliniii has compiled a list of groups that are collecting funds and dry rations to provide meals and aid to people that are effected in the north, east and central provinces. These people have been vetted by her; you can find her list in the google doc in my bio.

@affinityfoundationlk have opened a disaster relief meal center and are making packs for people affected. Visit their profile to see how you can help.

Other organizations that are raising funds and/or collecting dry rations donations:

@childactionlanka 

@adt.lanka 

@altrucirclex 

@palmeraprojects 

Visit their profiles to see how you can help.

If you have the name of any other organizations that are assisting in flood relief that, please feel free to tag them in the comments for people to find and support them.

#FloodRelief #CycloneDitwah

